summary: This appears to be a witness log and partial transcript from a grand jury proceeding in the state case against Jeffrey Epstein on July 19, 2006. It records the timing of witness testimony, cross-examination, and bench conferences involving defense and state attorneys.

events.title: Grand Jury Proceeding

keyFacts: The document is a witness log and partial transcript from a grand jury proceeding dated July 19, 2006.
The proceeding is part of a state criminal case against Jeffrey Epstein (case number referenced).
The log records the timing of witness testimony, cross-examination, redirect, re-cross, and bench conferences.
Attorneys for both the defense and the state (prosecution) were present and active, with a motion to strike noted.
The document is heavily redacted or garbled, making extraction of specific named individuals and detailed events impossible.
